WEBVTT

00:02.436 --> 00:15.010
The Nabhi chakra, is placed at the centre
of gravity, of every human being.

00:16.114 --> 00:20.738
If it is not there,

00:25.233 --> 00:31.532
that means it is going to be a little problem,

00:36.470 --> 00:41.679
for you to get it in its right place.

00:43.607 --> 00:56.712
There is a kind of a trouble which most of you suffer from,

00:59.783 --> 01:09.362
is maybe due to drugs or maybe nervous problems, due to war,

01:09.712 --> 01:16.783
or maybe some sort of a shock to your sustenance.

01:30.034 --> 01:40.527
For example, during war, people lost their values,

01:41.495 --> 01:47.870
because, they lost faith in God.

01:56.528 --> 02:09.410
Chaste women who believed in chastity,
were brutally assaulted.

02:19.349 --> 02:25.671
Very religious people, were persecuted,

02:30.552 --> 02:35.208
families were broken,

02:39.502 --> 02:43.899
many men were killed,

02:45.422 --> 02:56.863
and children, women, and old people, were scattered.

03:02.895 --> 03:08.510
A very horrible atmosphere of insecurity,

03:13.919 --> 03:17.735
overpowered all these nations.

03:22.918 --> 03:27.102
Then came the concentration camps, you see, also,

03:30.610 --> 03:37.283
which shattered human beings,

03:39.842 --> 03:47.581
because human beings are very delicate instruments.

03:52.263 --> 04:00.411
They are the coveted creations, they are the highest

04:03.828 --> 04:11.597
and they were dominated by things like bombs,
which are matter.

04:21.841 --> 04:30.875
Thus, the Spirit in man, died out.

04:35.958 --> 04:43.573
People lost faith in righteousness, in love.

04:54.210 --> 05:00.459
Then a new pattern of securities were built up.

05:07.078 --> 05:13.935
The industrial revolution followed it, as a result

05:23.689 --> 05:32.580
and the artificial sense of joy, of security, of love,

05:35.223 --> 05:39.706
was accepted by the society.

05:46.775 --> 05:50.184
This is what man did with his freedom,

05:50.644 --> 05:58.506
because wars are created by man, this is not Godâ€™s doing.

