06:37.004 --> 06:51.043
They started seeking beyond these artificial
securities, like materialism.

07:08.377 --> 07:13.589
The seekers had no proper leaders,

07:17.581 --> 07:22.114
to organize them,

07:25.566 --> 07:28.788
and to lead them to the right path.

07:30.599 --> 07:45.999
So the mistakes committed by them,
created a hurdle.

07:54.520 --> 07:58.432
So, apart from the hurdles of human awareness,

07:58.655 --> 08:02.940
so many other hurdles were added.

08:07.551 --> 08:16.907
So many other hurdles were added,
which made Sahaja Yoga a difficult process for them.

08:39.432 --> 08:49.982
The countries who took part in the war, only
became the developed countries.

08:50.704 --> 08:55.149
As a reaction, no its a reaction, they are
the only developed people,

08:56.151 --> 09:01.847
who are actually taking part in the war.

09:02.071 --> 09:06.870
