09:18.714 --> 09:30.208
So, on one side, we have countries,
who are trying to seek,

09:30.922 --> 09:39.443
because they are overdeveloped, because they are affluent,

09:44.982 --> 09:51.280
but their seekers have lost their moorings,

09:56.454 --> 10:01.660
because of anti-feeling.

10:10.170 --> 10:12.168
Alright?

10:13.985 --> 10:18.305
While other countries are not yet developed,

10:19.846 --> 10:27.305
so the seekers there, are still seeking in money.

10:42.853 --> 10:50.819
At this juncture, Sahaja Yoga was found out, this was the stage

11:01.591 --> 11:12.013
