11:19.380 --> 11:24.025
through which you feel your unconscious,

11:29.170 --> 11:35.163
the Power of God, which is All-pervading,

11:36.963 --> 11:42.933
which thinks, organizes, and plans.

11:56.870 --> 12:00.012
Only through Kundalini Yoga of Sahaja,

12:00.132 --> 12:04.989
Sahaja Kundalini Yoga, only through Sahaja Kundalini Yoga,

12:05.314 --> 12:10.634
human beings are going to evolve.

12:21.809 --> 12:25.839
